--- Problem ---
platform_service.go:187-196: $2 used for both broker_company SET and WHERE user_id,
isDisabled (6th arg) never referenced. Every call corrupted broker_company with user_id UUID.

--- Changes ---
1. MOD:  backend/internal/service/platform_service.go:187-196
   SQL renumbered: $1=id, $2=userID, $3=brokerCompany, $4=brokerServer, $5=brokerHost, $6=isDisabled
   Before: SET broker_company=$2, broker_server=$3, broker_host=$4, is_disabled=$5 WHERE $1 AND $2
   After:  SET broker_company=$3, broker_server=$4, broker_host=$5, is_disabled=$6 WHERE $1 AND $2

