3. NEW:  backend/migrations/121_repair_broker_company_corruption.down.sql
   No-op (data repair marker, not reversible).

4. NEW:  backend/internal/service/platform_update_account_integration_test.go
   Tests broker_company/broker_server/broker_host/is_disabled all correctly handled.

